@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qtxasi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos((0.14 + (tmp + 0.04 - v0 + 0.39)))
    v1 = v2
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.19 + v0 + 0.87) - 0.68))
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.25)) + wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.90)))
    v0 = (v0 * ((v0 + 0.59 / tmp + 0.25) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.48)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.40 + v2 + 0.25)) / wp.exp((tmp + 0.16 * v1 + 0.36)))
    data[tid] = v0
